INSTALL:
1. Install dbus and dbus-devel for your system
2. locate dbus include and library files
3. Create the CFLAGS and LDFLAGS holding the path to your dbus installation
   ex:
    export CFLAGS="-I/usr/include/dbus-1.0/ -I/usr/lib64/dbus-1.0/include/ -std=c99"
    export LDFLAGS="-L/usr/lib64/dbus-1.0/include/ -ldbus-1"
4. Run make
5. run ./spot_cli -h
